Package: simple-spot
Version: 1.0.2
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: raspotify (>= 0.47.0), bash, bluetooth
Maintainer: R. Moeijes <simpelmuis@gmail.com>
Description: Simple Spotify session watcher
 A minimal helper that monitors raspotify journal output and
 disconnects active Bluetooth devices on new Spotify sessions.
